This is a "now-playing" plugin for the Linkinus IRC client.

To install:

  1) Copy the radium script file to:
     ~/Library/Application Support/Linkinus 2/Scripts/

  2) Type "/radium" in the Linkinus IRC textbox and press Enter

Files in this directory were contributed by Don Jones from New Element
Designs (http://www.newelementdesigns.com).
